tafsir[8]{c,v,t}:
  5,96,"Daginanaama on yunngugol+raddugol kulle maayo Й—en, kala ko heЙ“otoo ka bahru -wuuri maayi- ko dakamme moo'on woni on ГұiiЙ“u maa hara on yooЙ“i e setewu. Harminanaama on waaГұugol ka njorndi (leydi) fodde hiЙ—on hormanii hajju maa 'umra. Hulee Alla, KO ka Makko woni ko mooЙ“oyteЙ—on Г‘alnde Darngal, O YoЙ“itoya on golle mon."
  5,97,"Alla WaЙ—ii Kaaba on : Suudu Hormante wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, maslaha maЙ“Й“e diina no huntee Й—on ; immorde e julde e hajju e 'umra, e maslaha aduna ; immorde e hoolaare nden ka haram e moЖҙЖҙere ko addetee ton. O WaЙ—i kadi lebbi hormante Й—in ГұiiЙ“irЙ—i wonannde Й“e, e neldaari ndin e ЕӢanneteeЙ—i=meedinaadi addee Й—in ka haram. Kon ko Alla Neemini e mon, ko fii yo on anndu wonnde Alla no Anndi kon ko woni ka kammuuli e ke leydi, e wonnde Alla no Anndi kala huunde ; tawde ko O Sar'ini kon ko fii Й“aЙ—nanngol on nafa duГұa lorra ado Й—um hewtude on, Й—um no tinndina wonnde himo Anndi ko moЖҙЖҙani JeyaaЙ“e Й“en."
  5,98,"Anndee, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, wonnde pellet, Alla ko SaЙ—tuЙ—o leptugol yeddoowo Mo, Haforanoowo on tuubanoowo Mo, HinnotooЙ—o."
  5,99,"Fawaaki NulaaЙ—o on si wanaa yottingol kon ko o Nulaa, wanaa kanko fawii fewnugol yimЙ“e Й“en, Й—um Й—on ko JuuЙ—e Alla tun woni. Alla no Anndi ko feГұГұinton e kon ko suuЙ—oton immorde e peewal maa majjere, O YoЙ“itoyay on Й—um."
  5,100,"Maaku, an NulaaЙ—o : "ko soЙ“i kon e ko laaЙ“i kon fotataa, hay si tawii non hawnii ma Й—uuЙ—ugol ko soЙ“i kon, tawde ngol Й—uuЙ—ugol hollaa Й“ural mun". Hulee Alla, onon joomiraaЙ“e haqqilaaji, tertoЙ—on ko soЙ“i jokkon ko laaЙ“i, belajo'o, on maliroyte Aljanna."
  5,101,"Ko onon gomЙ—imЙ“e ! wata on lamndo NulaaЙ—o mon on fii piiji Й—i alaa e haaju mon ka diina mon, tawa non si Й—in feГұГұinanaama on mettay on ko Й—i saЙ—tiri kon. Si on lamndino fii majji fewndo Qur'aanaare nden Jippotoo e NulaaЙ—o on, Й—i feГұГұinante on, Й—um ko ko newanii Alla. GomЙ—ii Alla Yawtanii gaay e piiji Й—i Qur'aana deЖҙЖҙi fii mun, wata on lamndo fii majji, si tawii le on lamndike fii majji, O Jippinay e mon Г‘aawooje majji."
  5,102,"GomЙ—ii yimЙ“e adinooЙ“e on lamndinoke fii majji, nde Й“e fawanoo Гұaawooje majji, Й“e wonti yedduЙ“e."
  5,103,"Alla Daginii neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, O Harminaali kon ko sirkooЙ“e Й“en harminanta ko'e-maЙ“Й“e fii sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in immorde e jelaaЙ—i Й—i Й“e taЖҙata noppi mun tuma Й—i rimi adadu=limoore heeriiЙ—o, e Й—in Й—i Й“e aacitiranta sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in tuma Й—i toowi e duuЙ“i, e Й—in jokkinrayЙ—i rimugol deyoy, wanaa kalaldi-wa, kono heeferЙ“e Й“en aaЖҙike fenaande e hoore Alla wonnde Й—in no harmi, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e Й“en yedduЙ“e, senndindiraa goonga e meere wanaa kadi ko harmi e dagii."